---
config:
    layout: elk
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant GUI as GUI/CLI
    participant Parser
    participant Builder
    participant PreMatcher
    participant Matcher as Matcher<br/>3-Tier
    participant Comparator
    participant Grader
    participant Reporter as Reporter/<br/>Visualizer
    participant FileSystem as File System

    User->>GUI: Submit solution + student files
    
    par Student Processing
        GUI->>Parser: Parse(studentFile)
        Parser->>FileSystem: Read .drawio
        FileSystem-->>Parser: Raw XML
        Parser-->>GUI: RawModelData
        
        GUI->>Builder: Build(rawData)
        Builder-->>GUI: UMLGraph
        
        GUI->>PreMatcher: Process(graph)
        Note over PreMatcher: Extract attributes,<br/>methods, edges
        PreMatcher-->>GUI: ProcessedUMLGraph
    and Solution Processing
        GUI->>Parser: Parse(solutionFile)
        Parser->>FileSystem: Read .solution
        FileSystem-->>Parser: Raw XML/JSON
        Parser-->>GUI: RawModelData
        
        GUI->>Builder: Build(rawData)
        Builder-->>GUI: UMLGraph
        
        GUI->>PreMatcher: ProcessSolution(graph)
        Note over PreMatcher: OR-aware parsing<br/>A|B|C aliases
        PreMatcher-->>GUI: SolutionProcessedUMLGraph
    end
    
    GUI->>Matcher: Match(solution, student)
    Note over Matcher: Tier 1: Architecture<br/>Tier 2: Fuzzy Names<br/>Tier 3: Delta
    Matcher-->>GUI: MappingTable
    
    GUI->>Comparator: Compare(solution, student, mapping)
    Note over Comparator: Node diff<br/>Attribute diff<br/>Method diff<br/>Edge diff
    Comparator-->>GUI: DiffReport
    
    GUI->>Grader: Grade(report, solution, student)
    Note over Grader: Calculate scores<br/>Generate feedbacks
    Grader-->>GUI: GradeResult
    
    par Output Generation
        Reporter->>FileSystem: Write CSV report
        Reporter-->>FileSystem: ✓ lab1_results.csv
    and
        Reporter->>FileSystem: Write HTML report
        Reporter-->>FileSystem: ✓ report.html
    end
    
    GUI-->>User: Display grade + feedback
    User->>FileSystem: Download reports